      private AbstractRegionPainter.PaintContext AbstractRegionPainter.ctx
      PaintContext, which holds a lot of the state needed for cache hinting and x/y value decoding The data contained within the context is typically only computed once and reused over multiple paint calls, whereas the other values (w, h, f, leftWidth, etc) are recomputed for each call to paint.
